\fs36 \cf0 Sorcerer
\fs22 \
The Sorcerer is a role that is completely devoted to magic.  They specialize in all the arcane arts except for healing.  They are useless with weapons, and may be weak in the beginning, but in higher ranks they are a dominating presence to be reckoned with.  A Sorcerer\'92s primary attribute is intelligence, but also consider speed for dodging attacks.  Luck never hurts a spell caster either...
