\fs36 \cf0 Cleric
\fs22 \
The Cleric is religious leader, focused on the magic of nature and all the various healing arts.  They are almost as devoted to magic as the Sorcerer, and over time will learn powerful spells of all kinds.  Most groups of adventurers find the restorative powers of the Cleric to be essential.  Having considerable charm also makes the Cleric ideal for negotiations, bartering, and diplomacy.  Primary attributes are charm and intelligence, but also consider speed for dodging attacks.  Luck never hurts a spell caster either...
\fs24 \
