\fs36 \cf0 Archer
\fs22 \
The Archer\'92s best friends are his bow, and his accuracy using it.  While an Archer can swing a sword if they need to, they get special bonuses for using projectile weapons, such as slings, blowpipes, and of course, the bow and arrow.  Having an Archer is helpful for fighting flying enemies.  The primary attributes of an Archer are accuracy and strength, but don\'92t discount speed and luck when using a bow...
