\fs36 \cf0 Bard
\fs22 \
The Bard is a jack of many trades.  They may not be the fastest, but they weave the arts of a Cleric, the spells of a Sorcerer, and sometimes even the brawn of a Knight into one role.  Most of their skill lies in magical song that aid their fellow adventurers and hamper enemies.  Due to their talents being spread out, Bards may not be powerful in the beginning, and inexperienced players may struggle to guide them in the early ranks.  Intelligence and Charm are most important to a Bard, but also consider strength if you want them to be warriors as well.
