\fs36 \cf0 Thief
\fs22 \
They are deplorable criminals, but every group of adventurers needs a Thief.  There will be locked doors and chests to pick open, and the need to steal back what is taken.  Some adventures are simply not available to a party without a Thief.  Luck and Speed are the Thief\'92s primary attributes, but also consider intelligence for the magic that will come with higher rank.
