\fs36 \cf0 Wolfen
\fs22 \
There is only one possible role for a Wolfen, and that is to be their loyal but vicious selves.  They grow into powerful beasts that crave the magic of moon and starlight.  Their growl will strike fear into your enemies, and send the weak fleeing for their lives.  But it is never wise to run from a Wolfen, because they love to chase down, trip, and then devour.  Consider strength and speed when crafting a Wolfen, but don\'92t forget intelligence for the magic that comes with higher rank.  Also consider the many advantages of having multiple Wolfens in your party.  A pack of Wolfens work together...
