\fs36 \cf0 Firebrand
\fs22 \
Firebrands are the classic bright red fire breathers of dragon legend.  There is magic in the fire that escapes their mouths, and it can do far more than just burn, such as destroying an enemy\'92s weapons and armor.  As rank increases, Firebrand dragons will also learn a few spells of their own.  Primary attributes are strength and intelligence.  While they will eventually learn to fly, consider a high speed attribute to dodge attacks.
